    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos domnus
                            <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/158">Gisolfus</persName> summus
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> gentis Langubardorum, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/2002" key="#Intercessory">Scauniperge</persName>
                        gloriosissima et dilecte coniugis nostre, in <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3413"
                            key="#Monasteries"> Beati Stephani</orgName> primi martyris qui fundatus
                        dinoscitur esse in <placeName ref="#places/3414"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property">Strata</placeName>, ubi
                            <persName ref="#people/3450" key="#Abbots">Rimecausus</persName>
                        reverentissimus <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> regimine tenere videtur, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >silba cum terra</rs> bacua qui fuit de <geogName
                            key="#Gai #Fiscal_property" ref="#estates/3408">gaio nostro in nominata
                            Strata</geogName>, id est de via in via et de alio latere usque in
                        strata maiore, de vero tertio latere usque in predicta ęcclesia Sancti
                        Stephani, qualiter nominata silba a <persName
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus #Actio" ref="#people/3495"
                            >Rotulo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs> nostro per nostram
                        iussionem vobis tradita est, qui fuit de <rs key="#Actio">acto</rs> nominati
                        Rotuli, quatenus amodo et deinceps habeas et possedeas tam tu qui supra
                        Rimecause quam et posteris vestris qui in prephato sacratissimo monasterio
                        ordinati fuerint, et nullus ex nostris gastaldiis aut actionariis vel
                        quisquam homo contraque nostra concessa potestas quandoque ire presumat, sed
                        nostra concessio omni in tempore roborea perhennis temporibus inviolata
                        permaneat. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex iussione et dictatu nominati
                        domni viri gloriosissimi Gisolfi scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"
                            ref="#people/3496">Prasinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum iussione in hunc sacratissimum
                            <placeName ref="#places/110" key="#Cities">Beneventanum</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Palatium">palatium</rs> mense novembrio per indictionem primam.
                        Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
